ion\"]\n    formalize_2 --> formalize_3[\"4. run_command<br/>cat the file to verify the write landed\"]\n    formalize_3 --> formalize_final([\"final answer<br/>the artifact inline\"])\n```\n\n## Part 3 — Recipe: Make a meaning more detailed (#538)\n\n```mermaid\nflowchart LR\n    meaning_task[\"user task<br/>(more detailed / grammatical number / a known concept)\"]\n    meaning_task --> meaning_0[\"1. web_search<br/>find the concept's Wikidata lexemes\"]\n    meaning_0 --> meaning_1[\"2. web_fetch<br/>read the forms; recover the missing plural\"]\n    meaning_1 --> meaning_2[\"3. write_file<br/>re-derive the grounded block, byte-for-byte the seed\"]\n    meaning_2 --> meaning_3[\"4. run_command<br/>cat the block to verify\"]\n    meaning_3 --> meaning_final([\"final answer<br/>the artifact inline\"])\n```\n\n## Part 4 — Recipe: Generate these diagrams (#538)\n\n```mermaid\nflowchart LR\n    diagram_task[\"user task<br/>(mermaid / diagram / visual overview)\"]\n    diagram_task --> diagram_0[\"1. write_file<br/>render the mermaid parts from the recipe table\"]\n    diagram_0 --> diagram_1[\"2. run_command<br/>cat the document to verify\"]\n    diagram_1 --> diagram_final([\"final answer<br/>the artifact inline\"])\n```\n\n## Part 5 — Recipe: Store the CST/AST of the meta algorithm (#538)\n\n```mermaid\nflowchart LR\n    self_ast_task[\"user task<br/>(cst/ast / abstract-syntax / reason about itself)\"]\n    self_ast_task --> self_ast_0[\"1. write_file<br/>parse the planner via meta-language; write the AST node census\"]\n    self_ast_0 --> self_ast_1[\"2. run_command<br/>cat the census to verify\"]\n    self_ast_1 --> self_ast_final([\"final answer<br/>the artifact inline\"])\n```\n","filePath":"agentic-recipes.md"}
